@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Gamma Wear";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <img src="~/images/gamma/gamma_wear.png" alt="Gamma Wear Company" class="img-fluid" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>
                Welcome to GammaWear, your premier destination for high-quality, stylish, and comfortable socks. Founded with a mission to blend fashion and function, GammaWear has become a trusted name in the sock industry, known for its commitment to excellence and innovation.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Corporate Headquarters</h2>
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>Our corporate headquarters is located in the vibrant city of Toronto, Ontario, Canada. This strategic location allows us to stay at the forefront of fashion trends and technological advancements, ensuring that we offer our customers the best products available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/gamma/gammawear_building.png" alt="GammaWear Corporate Headquarters" class="about-image" />
        </div>

    </div>
    <h2>Our Team</h2>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>GammaWear boasts a dedicated team of professionals who are passionate about delivering the finest socks to our customers. Our staff includes experienced designers, skilled artisans, and a dynamic marketing team, all working together to create and promote our unique sock collections. We believe in fostering a collaborative and inclusive work environment, which helps us stay creative and ahead of the curve.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Our Products</h2>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>At GammaWear, we understand that socks are more than just a basic necessity; they are an expression of personal style and comfort. Our product range includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Casual Socks:</strong> Perfect for everyday wear, our casual socks come in a variety of colors and patterns, offering both comfort and style.</li>
                <li><strong>Athletic Socks:</strong> Designed for performance, our athletic socks provide the support and breathability needed for any sport or physical activity.</li>
                <li><strong>Dress Socks:</strong> Elevate your formal attire with our elegant dress socks, available in classic designs and sophisticated colors.</li>
                <li><strong>Outdoor and Adventure Socks:</strong> Whether you’re hiking, camping, or skiing, our outdoor socks are built to withstand the elements and keep your feet warm and dry.</li>
                <li><strong>Eco-Friendly Options:</strong> We are committed to sustainability and offer a range of eco-friendly socks made from organic and recycled materials.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">

            <p>GammaWear is dedicated to customer satisfaction and environmental responsibility. We source the finest materials and employ rigorous quality control measures to ensure that every pair of socks meets our high standards. Our eco-friendly initiatives include reducing waste, using sustainable materials, and supporting environmental causes.</p>

            <p>Join us on our journey to revolutionize the sock industry with style, comfort, and innovation. Discover the perfect pair of socks at GammaWear, where your feet are our priority.</p>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>

